 navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Hedge_Knight_(comics)\" title=\"The Hedge Knight (comics)\">The Hedge Knight</a></i>\n<ul><li><i>The Hedge Knight</i></li>\n<li><i>The Hedge Knight II: Sworn Sword</i></li>\n<li><i>The Mystery Knight</i></li></ul></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones_(comics)\" title=\"A Game of Thrones (comics)\">A Game of Thrones</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings_(comics)\" title=\"A Clash of Kings (comics)\">A Clash of Kings</a></i></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Other publications</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li>Art collection: <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Art_of_George_R._R._Martin%27s_A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Art of George R. R. Martin&#39;s A Song of Ice and Fire\">The Art of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li>App: <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">A World of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li>Blog: <i><a href=\"/index.php/Not_A_Blog\" title=\"Not A Blog\">Not A Blog</a></i></li>\n<li>Correspondence: <a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a></li>\n<li>Yearly calendars: <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Calendar\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li>Scholarly: <i><a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall_(Book)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Beyond the Wall (Book)\">Beyond the Wall</a></i></li>\n<li>Cookbook: <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Feast of Ice and Fire\">A Feast of Ice and Fire</a></i></li>\n<li>Parody: <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Groans\" title=\"A Game of Groans\">A Game of Groans</a></i></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr